{"ja433:0.1":"Jataka ","ja433:0.2":"Navakanipata ","ja433:0.3":"Gijjhavagga ","ja433:0.4":"7. Lomasakassapajataka ","ja433:1.1":"“Assa indasamo raja, ","ja433:1.2":"accantam ajaramaro; ","ja433:1.3":"Sace tvam yannam yajeyya, ","ja433:1.4":"isim lomasakassapam”. ","ja433:2.1":"“Sasamuddapariyayam, ","ja433:2.2":"mahim sagarakundalam; ","ja433:2.3":"Na icche saha nindaya, ","ja433:2.4":"evam seyya vijanahi. ","ja433:3.1":"Dhiratthu tam yasalabham, ","ja433:3.2":"dhanalabhanca brahmana; ","ja433:3.3":"Ya vutti vinipatena, ","ja433:3.4":"adhammacaranena va. ","ja433:4.1":"Api ce pattamadaya, ","ja433:4.2":"anagaro paribbaje; ","ja433:4.3":"Sayeva jivika seyyo, ","ja433:4.4":"ya cadhammena esana. ","ja433:5.1":"Api ce pattamadaya, ","ja433:5.2":"anagaro paribbaje; ","ja433:5.3":"Annam ahimsayam loke, ","ja433:5.4":"api rajjena tam varam”. ","ja433:6.1":"“Balam cando balam suriyo, ","ja433:6.2":"balam samanabrahmana; ","ja433:6.3":"Balam vela samuddassa, ","ja433:6.4":"balatibalamitthiyo. ","ja433:7.1":"Yatha uggatapam santam, ","ja433:7.2":"isim lomasakassapam; ","ja433:7.3":"Pitu attha candavati, ","ja433:7.4":"vajapeyyam ayajayi”. ","ja433:8.1":"“Tam lobhapakatam kammam, ","ja433:8.2":"Katukam kamahetukam; ","ja433:8.3":"Tassa mulam gavesissam, ","ja433:8.4":"Checcham ragam sabandhanam. ","ja433:9.1":"Dhiratthu kame subahupi loke, ","ja433:9.2":"Tapova seyyo kamagunehi raja; ","ja433:9.3":"Tapo karissami pahaya kame, ","ja433:9.4":"Taveva rattham candavati ca hotu”ti. ","ja433:10.1":"Lomasakassapajatakam sattamam. "}